lead_paragraph: Monique Billings scored 18 points and grabbed eight rebounds, and No. 12 UCLA raced past Arizona for a 72-51 win in the Pac-12 tournament quarterfinals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Billings Leads No. 12 UCLA Past Arizona 72-51.
